Package: documentNumbering
Type: Package
Title: Functions for Numbering in Documents
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person(given = c("Robert", "M"), family = "Flight", email
        = "rflight79@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides a framework for numbering in Rmd and other files where
  automatic numbering normally isn't provided.
  Rmd -> Word as one example where there normally isn't any automatic figure numbering.
